<font color="yellow">I'm going to divorce Jeong Ae.</font>

632
00:41:51,025 --> 00:41:52,225
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

633
00:41:54,135 --> 00:41:56,295
<font color="yellow">- What did you say he said? - He said..</font>

634
00:41:57,265 --> 00:41:59,565
<font color="yellow">we should get our pensions in advance,</font>

635
00:42:00,425 --> 00:42:03,865
<font color="yellow">and open up a shop for Seong Hoon with that money.</font>

636
00:42:03,925 --> 00:42:07,525
<font color="yellow">Why is he talking about opening up a shop all of a sudden?</font>

637
00:42:07,565 --> 00:42:10,635
<font color="yellow">He said Seong Hoon will have to spend more money...</font>

638
00:42:10,635 --> 00:42:13,465
<font color="yellow">to educate Ji Hoon now. When I said no,</font>

639
00:42:13,565 --> 00:42:15,965
<font color="yellow">he said he will divorce me.</font>

640
00:42:16,095 --> 00:42:17,165
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

641
00:42:17,365 --> 00:42:20,065
<font color="yellow">He will divorce me, sell this place, split the money,</font>

642
00:42:20,135 --> 00:42:21,965
<font color="yellow">and open up a shop for Seong Hoon.</font>

643
00:42:22,225 --> 00:42:24,895
<font color="yellow">Mother. Can you believe that?</font>

644
00:42:25,965 --> 00:42:27,925
<font color="yellow">He called me a witch...</font>

645
00:42:28,095 --> 00:42:29,895
<font color="yellow">because I'm mean to my children.</font>

646
00:42:30,765 --> 00:42:32,995
<font color="yellow">How can we survive if I'm not?</font>

647
00:42:33,225 --> 00:42:37,135
<font color="yellow">All we've got left is our pensions. How can I let him cancel it?</font>

648
00:42:37,265 --> 00:42:39,865
<font color="yellow">But he's being so stubborn and unreasonable.</font>

649
00:42:39,895 --> 00:42:42,765
<font color="yellow">He's just crazy about his children, Mother.</font>

650
00:42:42,825 --> 00:42:44,295
<font color="yellow">Gosh, this is driving me crazy.</font>

651
00:42:44,495 --> 00:42:47,825
<font color="yellow">We solve one problem, and another problem comes up.</font>

652
00:42:48,195 --> 00:42:51,025
<font color="yellow">It's all because we're all living in the same building.</font>

653
00:42:51,195 --> 00:42:52,595
<font color="yellow">That's what I'm saying.</font>

654
00:43:23,425 --> 00:43:24,525
<font color="yellow">You brat.</font>

655
00:43:26,425 --> 00:43:28,965
<font color="yellow">Of course. I knew you'd be okay.</font>

656
00:43:31,095 --> 00:43:34,565
<font color="yellow">You're a strong and optimistic boy.</font>

657
00:43:44,265 --> 00:43:45,265
<font color="yellow">Chang Soo.</font>

658
00:43:46,025 --> 00:43:47,765
<font color="yellow">I'm still sorry to you.</font>

659
00:44:56,225 --> 00:44:58,295
<font color="yellow">Mom. I'm here.</font>

660
00:44:59,195 --> 00:45:00,525
<font color="yellow">Where are you?</font>

661
00:45:02,395 --> 00:45:03,695
<font color="yellow">Is she in her room?</font>

662
00:45:11,495 --> 00:45:12,995
<font color="yellow">Oh, my.</font>

663
00:45:18,425 --> 00:45:19,595
<font color="yellow">You're here.</font>

664
00:45:20,925 --> 00:45:21,925
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

665
00:45:22,165 --> 00:45:24,765
<font color="yellow">Mom. What on earth are you doing?</font>

666
00:45:24,765 --> 00:45:25,795
<font color="yellow">What am I doing?</font>

667
00:45:25,795 --> 00:45:29,565
<font color="yellow">How can you bring a man into your house at your age?</font>

668
00:45:29,695 --> 00:45:32,425
<font color="yellow">- I don't do that myself. - My gosh. You silly thing.</font>

669
00:45:32,495 --> 00:45:35,795
<font color="yellow">Go inside and take a look. He's someone you know.</font>

670
00:45:36,995 --> 00:45:38,025
<font color="yellow">Someone I know?</font>

671
00:45:52,995 --> 00:45:54,065
<font color="yellow">Hyung Seop.</font>

672
00:45:58,695 --> 00:46:00,965
<font color="yellow">I was startled to see my grandchildren...</font>

673
00:46:00,965 --> 00:46:02,765
<font color="yellow">move back in after all those years.</font>

674
00:46:02,795 --> 00:46:05,495
<font color="yellow">Goodness. My own child has come back home again.</font>

675
00:46:05,495 --> 00:46:07,765
<font color="yellow">Who would have imagined he would become a kangaroo and return?</font>

676
00:46:08,395 --> 00:46:09,425
<font color="yellow">Hyung Seop.</font>

677
00:46:10,025 --> 00:46:12,165
<font color="yellow">You should go back to your house.</font>

678
00:46:12,525 --> 00:46:13,525
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

679
00:46:14,165 --> 00:46:15,695
<font color="yellow">I'm divorcing Jeong Ae.</font>

680
00:46:16,165 --> 00:46:18,495
<font color="yellow">If you divorce her, whom are you going to live with?</font>

681
00:46:18,995 --> 00:46:20,825
<font color="yellow">Me? I don't want that.</font>

682
00:46:20,895 --> 00:46:23,095
<font color="yellow">Gosh. You're so mean, Mom.</font>

683
00:46:23,095 --> 00:46:26,265
<font color="yellow">My gosh. Do you expect me to feed my son at this age?</font>

684
00:46:26,265 --> 00:46:27,795
<font color="yellow">I'll feed myself.</font>

685
00:46:27,795 --> 00:46:30,195
<font color="yellow">No. I don't want to see you,</font>

686
00:46:30,365 --> 00:46:33,495
<font color="yellow">and I don't want people to misunderstand. Go back downstairs.</font>

687
00:46:33,795 --> 00:46:34,925
<font color="yellow">Why would people misunderstand?</font>

688
00:46:35,595 --> 00:46:37,825
<font color="yellow">Ae Ri saw you sleeping,</font>

689
00:46:37,925 --> 00:46:40,695
<font color="yellow">and thought I brought a man into my house.</font>

690
00:46:41,125 --> 00:46:42,225
<font color="yellow">How silly.</font>

691
00:46:43,665 --> 00:46:46,795
<font color="yellow">I guess you're not Mom's type.</font>

692
00:46:46,795 --> 00:46:48,425
<font color="yellow">Stop talking nonsense.</font>

693
00:46:48,565 --> 00:46:51,425
<font color="yellow">So please go back to your house.</font>

694
00:46:51,495 --> 00:46:54,065
<font color="yellow">This is absurd. You're not newlyweds.</font>

695
00:46:54,065 --> 00:46:57,025
<font color="yellow">Forget it. I'm fully determined this time.</font>

696
00:46:57,625 --> 00:47:00,665
<font color="yellow">I'm not going to live with that woman anymore.</font>

697
00:47:00,695 --> 00:47:02,495
<font color="yellow">Go back downstairs! I was sleeping last night,</font>

698
00:47:02,495 --> 00:47:05,725
<font color="yellow">and I got startled because I saw you and I thought you were a goblin.</font>

699
00:47:11,295 --> 00:47:13,695
<font color="yellow">Ae Ri. Take that...</font>

700
00:47:14,495 --> 00:47:16,125
<font color="yellow">ginseng preserve.</font>

701
00:47:16,125 --> 00:47:18,665
<font color="yellow">Give it to Jeong Ae,</font>

702
00:47:18,725 --> 00:47:22,595
<font color="yellow">and curry favor with her. Say it'll boost her immune system.</font>

703
00:47:23,195 --> 00:47:26,065
<font color="yellow">If he divorces her, it will give us so much trouble.</font>

704
00:47:26,095 --> 00:47:27,625
<font color="yellow">I know.</font>

705
00:47:29,025 --> 00:47:30,095
<font color="yellow">Hyung Seop.</font>

706
00:47:30,665 --> 00:47:32,695
<font color="yellow">You should eat some of it as well, okay?</font>

707
00:47:32,695 --> 00:47:35,325
<font color="yellow">It will melt away the old grudge between you two.</font>

708
00:47:35,995 --> 00:47:38,225
<font color="yellow">Everything will be melted down...</font>

709
00:47:38,265 --> 00:47:39,825
<font color="yellow">like the snow.</font>

710
00:47:39,825 --> 00:47:41,125
<font color="yellow">- Look. - That's right.</font>

711
00:47:46,565 --> 00:47:47,795
<font color="yellow">Hyung Seop!</font>

712
00:47:50,465 --> 00:47:53,195
<font color="yellow">Mother, what are you talking about?</font>

713
00:47:53,225 --> 00:47:54,965
<font color="yellow">Don't you get it?</font>

714
00:47:56,995 --> 00:47:59,295
<font color="yellow">I have never heard of this.</font>

715
00:47:59,525 --> 00:48:03,225
<font color="yellow">What I'm saying is if you asked your father-in-law...</font>

716
00:48:03,425 --> 00:48:05,765
<font color="yellow">to help you financially to open you a shop.</font>

717
00:48:05,925 --> 00:48:08,025
<font color="yellow">No, Mother, no.</font>

718
00:48:08,195 --> 00:48:11,595
<font color="yellow">Why would your father-in-law say that suddenly, then?</font>

719
00:48:11,695 --> 00:48:13,595
<font color="yellow">I have no idea.</font>

720
00:48:13,625 --> 00:48:15,825
<font color="yellow">Aren't you pretending not to know everything even though you do?</font>

721
00:48:15,965 --> 00:48:18,595
<font color="yellow">- Mother! - Do you think I don't know...</font>

722
00:48:18,825 --> 00:48:21,895
<font color="yellow">that you get allowance from your father-in-law every now and then?</font>

723
00:48:23,365 --> 00:48:24,865
<font color="yellow">Mother,</font>

724
00:48:25,295 --> 00:48:26,895
<font color="yellow">that's something he gave me once.</font>

725
00:48:26,925 --> 00:48:30,265
<font color="yellow">The number of times is not what matters. Would you want to get...</font>

726
00:48:30,265 --> 00:48:33,365
<font color="yellow">allowance from your old parents-in-law, not give?</font>

727
00:48:34,295 --> 00:48:37,865
<font color="yellow">Sure, you can get allowance.</font>

728
00:48:37,895 --> 00:48:40,025
<font color="yellow">However, it's too much to ask him to help you...</font>

729
00:48:40,195 --> 00:48:42,725
<font color="yellow">to open the shop with our pension.</font>

730
00:48:42,825 --> 00:48:45,295
<font color="yellow">We already let you live downstairs.</font>

731
00:48:45,295 --> 00:48:48,495
<font color="yellow">Must we open the coffee shop for you with our pension?</font>

732
00:48:49,525 --> 00:48:53,365
<font color="yellow">Mother, that's not true. I really didn't do that.</font>

733
00:48:53,425 --> 00:48:55,665
<font color="yellow">Whether you've done it or not, that's what you do.</font>

734
00:48:56,065 --> 00:48:59,395
<font color="yellow">That's why you lived for 15 years without knowing your child's switch.</font>

735
00:49:01,825 --> 00:49:04,065
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about, Mother?</font>

736
00:49:04,225 --> 00:49:07,025
<font color="yellow">You don't take care of housework and keep going outside.</font>

737
00:49:07,025 --> 00:49:09,295
<font color="yellow">That's why your house and your child's like that.</font>

738
00:49:09,365 --> 00:49:11,965
<font color="yellow">You got depressed soon as your husband lost his job.</font>

739
00:49:11,965 --> 00:49:14,665
<font color="yellow">Is there anything you do right?</font>

740
00:49:14,725 --> 00:49:15,725
<font color="yellow">Mother,</font>

741
00:49:16,225 --> 00:49:20,165
<font color="yellow">you can't talk about Ji Hoon and Chang Soo like that.</font>

742
00:49:20,295 --> 00:49:23,295
<font color="yellow">Did I make anything up? Look at Hee Sook.</font>

743
00:49:23,525 --> 00:49:25,365
<font color="yellow">She raised her son to be the first student at school,</font>

744
00:49:25,365 --> 00:49:28,765
<font color="yellow">but you have raised your son as the last one.</font>

745
00:49:28,825 --> 00:49:32,765
<font color="yellow">If you switch the two of them now, she will find it preposterous.</font>

746
00:49:32,965 --> 00:49:33,965
<font color="yellow">Mother.</font>

747
00:49:34,595 --> 00:49:37,425
<font color="yellow">At least I raised Chang Soo with love.</font>

748
00:49:38,065 --> 00:49:41,365
<font color="yellow">I never wanted to switch him with Ji Hoon.</font>

749
00:49:41,395 --> 00:49:44,425
<font color="yellow">Then tell Hee Sook to raise Ji Hoon.</font>

750
00:49:44,525 --> 00:49:48,195
<font color="yellow">Don't make him become the last student at school.</font>

751
00:49:48,365 --> 00:49:50,565
<font color="yellow">- Mother! - Anyway,</font>

752
00:49:50,895 --> 00:49:54,595
<font color="yellow">we can't open the shop for you.</font>

753
00:49:54,725 --> 00:49:56,065
<font color="yellow">Just so you know.</font>

754
00:50:09,295 --> 00:50:10,295
<font color="yellow">Hye Joo.</font>

755
00:50:12,595 --> 00:50:13,595
<font color="yellow">Grandma.</font>

756
00:50:13,995 --> 00:50:16,065
<font color="yellow">Grandma, Grandma.</font>

757
00:50:16,825 --> 00:50:17,965
<font color="yellow">What's the matter?</font>

758
00:50:18,965 --> 00:50:21,065
<font color="yellow">Grandma, I can no longer live like this.</font>

759
00:50:21,295 --> 00:50:24,895
<font color="yellow">I can't live with my mother-in-law.</font>

760
00:50:25,365 --> 00:50:26,365
<font color="yellow">My gosh,</font>

761
00:50:26,725 --> 00:50:30,265
<font color="yellow">you shouldn't run upstairs like this, though.</font>

762
00:50:33,125 --> 00:50:36,465
<font color="yellow">There's limit to insisting...</font>

763
00:50:36,525 --> 00:50:38,165
<font color="yellow">nonsense.</font>

764
00:50:38,795 --> 00:50:41,165
<font color="yellow">She says I convinced my father...</font>

765
00:50:41,165 --> 00:50:44,165
<font color="yellow">to open the shop for me.</font>

766
00:50:44,295 --> 00:50:46,995
<font color="yellow">What is she talking about?</font>

767
00:50:47,065 --> 00:50:49,265
<font color="yellow">I have no idea. I really don't know.</font>

768
00:50:49,265 --> 00:50:51,765
<font color="yellow">Whenever something comes up,</font>

769
00:50:51,765 --> 00:50:54,725
<font color="yellow">my mother blames me.</font>

770
00:50:55,295 --> 00:50:56,595
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

771
00:50:58,065 --> 00:50:59,265
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear.</font>

772
00:51:01,265 --> 00:51:03,395
<font color="yellow">Hye Joo, don't cry.</font>

773
00:51:03,925 --> 00:51:06,025
<font color="yellow">Crying would make you even more upset.</font>

774
00:51:08,165 --> 00:51:09,425
<font color="yellow">Grandma.</font>

775
00:51:11,295 --> 00:51:12,625
<font color="yellow">Grandma, I...</font>

776
00:51:13,695 --> 00:51:16,025
<font color="yellow">I can't live here anymore.</font>

777
00:51:18,665 --> 00:51:22,565
<font color="yellow">I really want to move out, Grandma.</font>

778
00:51:23,365 --> 00:51:25,425
<font color="yellow">I am so bitter at Seong Hoon,</font>

779
00:51:26,195 --> 00:51:29,595
<font color="yellow">I don't get why I moved in with my parents-in-law.</font>

780
00:51:30,095 --> 00:51:33,995
<font color="yellow">There is no single day when my mind is at ease.</font>

781
00:51:51,995 --> 00:51:53,125
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui,</font>

782
00:51:54,725 --> 00:51:55,765
<font color="yellow">what are you doing?</font>

783
00:51:56,395 --> 00:51:57,895
<font color="yellow">Nothing.</font>

784
00:51:59,295 --> 00:52:00,765
<font color="yellow">You're so boring.</font>

785
00:52:00,995 --> 00:52:03,665
<font color="yellow">You're young, but you're not doing anything on Christmas Eve.</font>

786
00:52:03,695 --> 00:52:05,295
<font color="yellow">Does it even make any sense?</font>

787
00:52:05,795 --> 00:52:07,625
<font color="yellow">That's why I came to get you.</font>

788
00:52:08,365 --> 00:52:10,795
<font color="yellow">- Let's go. - Where to?</font>

789
00:52:11,095 --> 00:52:13,365
<font color="yellow">I'm opening my coffee shop today.</font>

790
00:52:13,465 --> 00:52:14,995
<font color="yellow">Gosh, really?</font>

791
00:52:15,465 --> 00:52:19,365
<font color="yellow">I'm throwing an opening ceremony and Christmas party in the evening.</font>

792
00:52:19,825 --> 00:52:21,965
<font color="yellow">I hope you can give me a hand.</font>

793
00:52:23,295 --> 00:52:24,465
<font color="yellow">Shall I?</font>

794
00:52:25,795 --> 00:52:29,465
<font color="yellow">What a cozy and cute place.</font>

795
00:52:29,465 --> 00:52:30,495
<font color="yellow">You think so, right?</font>

796
00:52:32,025 --> 00:52:35,365
<font color="yellow">I did all the dcor on my own.</font>

797
00:52:35,465 --> 00:52:36,565
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

798
00:52:38,865 --> 00:52:40,525
<font color="yellow">Well, someone helped me a bit.</font>

799
00:52:41,665 --> 00:52:42,895
<font color="yellow">Is that so?</font>

800
00:52:44,895 --> 00:52:45,995
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

801
00:52:46,795 --> 00:52:50,095
<font color="yellow">You should ask who it was. I'm dying to tell you.</font>

802
00:52:52,295 --> 00:52:55,225
<font color="yellow">- Who helped you? - There's someone.</font>

803
00:52:59,295 --> 00:53:01,695
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui, don't you like anyone?</font>

804
00:53:05,295 --> 00:53:06,465
<font color="yellow">I don't.</font>

805
00:53:06,565 --> 00:53:10,295
<font color="yellow">Right, there's no way a woman sitting on a rooftop on...</font>

806
00:53:10,295 --> 00:53:11,765
<font color="yellow">Christmas Eve has a boyfriend.</font>

807
00:53:12,825 --> 00:53:15,195
<font color="yellow">Do you have someone you like, then?</font>

808
00:53:17,895 --> 00:53:20,195
<font color="yellow">- Yes. - Who is it?</font>

809
00:53:24,695 --> 00:53:26,095
<font color="yellow">He'll be here later.</font>

810
00:53:30,965 --> 00:53:33,225
<font color="yellow">- Should I turn it? - Yes, let's work on the back.</font>

811
00:53:40,025 --> 00:53:42,265
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon, shall we have another glass of wine?</font>

812
00:53:44,395 --> 00:53:45,565
<font color="yellow">Let me pour it for you.</font>

813
00:53:50,125 --> 00:53:51,165
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

814
00:54:05,225 --> 00:54:06,825
<font color="yellow">Let's have a toast.</font>

815
00:54:10,825 --> 00:54:12,265
<font color="yellow">Merry Christmas.</font>

816
00:54:19,765 --> 00:54:23,725
<font color="yellow">It's been a while since we spent Christmas Eve together, right?</font>

817
00:54:24,365 --> 00:54:25,365
<font color="yellow">Has it?</font>

818
00:54:26,065 --> 00:54:28,195
<font color="yellow">Here it goes again. You're so inattentive.</font>

819
00:54:28,895 --> 00:54:32,795
<font color="yellow">You're an inattentive man who can't remember a single memory.</font>

820
00:54:36,195 --> 00:54:39,525
<font color="yellow">- Mi Joo. - Why do you suddenly look serious?</font>

821
00:54:41,795 --> 00:54:44,025
<font color="yellow">Don't do that. I'm scared.</font>

822
00:54:44,665 --> 00:54:46,925
<font color="yellow">I'm not scared of my dad,</font>

823
00:54:47,195 --> 00:54:49,625
<font color="yellow">but I am scared of you so often.</font>

824
00:54:49,965 --> 00:54:51,695
<font color="yellow">Why are you scared of me?</font>

825
00:54:52,765 --> 00:54:53,925
<font color="yellow">It's because I like you.</font>

826
00:54:54,465 --> 00:54:57,165
<font color="yellow">People are normally scared in front of those they like.</font>

827
00:54:57,965 --> 00:54:59,195
<font color="yellow">I hope...</font>

828
00:55:03,095 --> 00:55:05,095
<font color="yellow">you won't be scared of me.</font>

829
00:55:08,095 --> 00:55:09,465
<font color="yellow">I hope you'll always be dignified...</font>

830
00:55:11,865 --> 00:55:13,095
<font color="yellow">and sure of yourself.</font>

831
00:55:13,965 --> 00:55:15,525
<font color="yellow">I hope you'll be someone like that.</font>

832
00:55:16,295 --> 00:55:17,395
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

833
00:55:18,265 --> 00:55:20,425
<font color="yellow">- Mi Joo. - Stop it.</font>

834
00:55:20,425 --> 00:55:22,425
<font color="yellow">What are you trying to say?</font>

835
00:55:22,765 --> 00:55:23,825
<font color="yellow">We have...</font>

836
00:55:26,065 --> 00:55:27,825
<font color="yellow">seen each other for the past five years.</font>

837
00:55:29,125 --> 00:55:30,765
